Let name be "Prose Language".
Say "Testing advanced features of " plus name plus ":".

Let age be 20.
If age >= 18 then do the following.
    Say "You are an adult.".
End if.

Let number be 5.
Say "The number is " plus number plus ".".

Let a be 15.
Let b be 4.
Let result1 be a plus b.
Let result2 be a minus b.
Let result3 be a times b.
Let result4 be a divided by b.
Say "Result of addition is " plus result1 plus ".".
Say "Result of subtraction is " plus result2 plus ".".
Say "Result of multiplication is " plus result3 plus ".".
Say "Result of division is " plus result4 plus ".".

Let greeting be "Hello, World!".
Say "Original: " plus greeting plus ".".